# Instructions for key management:
# 1. Generate work-specific GPG key: gpg --gen-key
# 2. Add key to git-crypt: git-crypt add-gpg-user FINGERPRINT
# 3. Export public key for backup: gpg --export --armor FINGERPRINT > work-key.asc
# 4. Store symmetric key securely for fallback access

# Symmetric key backup instructions:
# - The symmetric key is stored in .git/git-crypt/keys/default
# - Back up this key securely for recovery purposes
# - Use: git-crypt export-key /path/to/backup/key.bin